Need to built an Insulin factory just because of this shit. For all of you who don't know about Insulin, Insulin is a peptide hormone made and secreted by the pancreas to cause excess glucose to be taken up from the blood, thereby lowering blood-glucose levels that could otherwise be toxic. Insulin is made in beta cells, which cluster into islets. When glucose arrives at the pancreas via capillaries, insulin is released from the beta cells into the bloodstream where it then travels to it’s target organs, primarily the liver, muscle and fat. Insulin binds to insulin receptors on target cells, stimulating the cells to express glucose transporters on the cell membrane for uptake of glucose. Glucose is then stored within the cell for later use.
